  <article class="entry h-entry hentry category-reviewing tag-boyd tag-marine-corps tag-maneuver tag-reform author-dan-grazier post-type-text has-main-image clear" id="article-5c9bee2971c10b134dfce47d" data-item-id="5c9bee2971c10b134dfce47d">

    <header class="entry-header">
      <div class="meta-above-title">
        
        <div class="entry-byline">
          <span class="entry-author"><a href="/the-bridge?author=5c616ecc53450a883a2cc5dd" class="p-author author entry-byline-link" rel="author">Dan Grazier</a></span>
